normal people wouldn't think this way.

124
00:12:04,433 --> 00:12:06,867
Your grades for the
college of medicine are As.

125
00:12:06,967 --> 00:12:09,733
But... I want to do painting.

126
00:12:10,667 --> 00:12:13,300
Or you might take painting as a hobby.

127
00:12:13,392 --> 00:12:15,859
You should hold on to the chance
to go to a good college,

128
00:12:15,967 --> 00:12:17,933
then you can take the things
you like as hobbies.

129
00:12:19,433 --> 00:12:21,867
If you know what I mean,
just go back to rewrite it.

130
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:33,100
I think there's no need for everyone
to go for the same route.

131
00:12:33,767 --> 00:12:36,033
What are you talking about? Miss Misaki

132
00:12:36,133 --> 00:12:37,533
I'm sorry for interrupting.

133
00:12:38,775 --> 00:12:42,275
But something like this shouldn't
be thought of as a norm to follow.

134
00:12:42,367 --> 00:12:45,933
We should think about the future life
of the students as well.

135
00:12:48,667 --> 00:12:50,859
If you really have something
you want to achieve...

136
00:12:51,400 --> 00:12:52,433
Just go for it.

137
00:12:54,633 --> 00:12:55,533
Yes.

138
