How's going? How long since we met?

139
00:13:04,833 --> 00:13:09,300
It's been three years since I graduated.

140
00:13:10,067 --> 00:13:11,500
How are you doing right now?

141
00:13:12,367 --> 00:13:13,567
I'm doing just fine.

142
00:13:13,682 --> 00:13:15,648
How about painting? Do you do painting now?

143
00:13:15,733 --> 00:13:16,533
