147
00:13:25,233 --> 00:13:28,100
You mean that "eshi"?
It's old-school to say so.

148
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,633
An old-school saying?

149
00:13:29,733 --> 00:13:32,400
It should be called "illustrator" now.

150
00:13:32,507 --> 00:13:35,640
Ah... I am still way behind that.

151
00:13:35,733 --> 00:13:39,133
Although I do illustration on the internet
it's not what I can count on for a living.

152
00:13:40,433 --> 00:13:42,667
Ah... you've got some stains here...

153
00:13:44,733 --> 00:13:45,767
Thank you.

154
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:48,867
That guy was really going too far.

155
00:13:50,882 --> 00:13:53,633
Shyuuhei, I really appreciate what you've done.

156
00:13:53,733 --> 00:13:55,333
But never do it again.

157
00:13:55,433 --> 00:13:57,867
It's lucky that you are fine now, but
there're many strange people nowadays.

158
00:13:58,233 --> 00:14:01,633
Why? I'm just being honest to myself.

159
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:04,767
